platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: A comic book fans dream, Marvel Strike Force lets you build the ultimate team of heroes and villains, then face enemy crews in breathtaking strategic battles. Can the Sinister Six withstand Human Torchs supernova? Will Star-Lords dancing distract the X-Men long enough for Ultron to finish them off? Whether youre braving deep story missions or buddying up in riveting Alliance Wars, youll love playing with Marvels mightiest. Excelsior!
